{"tid":1948424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想做增高手術，唔想人生就咁玩完，好似好正咁！","createTime":"2020-03-29T04:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T23:14:54.000Z","uid":329324,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab40292954325b7f819d938bb0642d282360739","tid":1948424,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQdvNEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQdvNEF.png&h=ff62be58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mG709S3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmG709S3.png&h=4f5ac00f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Du6pR6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDu6pR6q.png&h=52ebb48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最衰on 9老母唔識教仔又學人生bb ,搞到我細細個既時候根本無人理，長大後讀到大學都無乜用，想遲下自費拎100萬做呢一個增高手術，痛都唔介意...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問有無人都有興趣做增高手術，我見佢講到好輕鬆咁，痛一年就已經增到高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之真係好想同呢個唔識教仔既老母絕交，佢死左都唔想再拜佢。<br />\n<br />\n搞到我人生咁撚差，而家儲錢想遲下用一百萬做呢個手術提高身高。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打都做過同一手術？"},{"pid":"974cdee1c9252aa54cede123fa156132c01f669d","tid":1948424,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRRYb7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRRYb7B.png&h=f5328862&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMg5Bzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMg5Bzi.png&h=6e4e3e51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a47ee7d49b78d48aeff8431800dd8c37ec234f08","tid":1948424,"uid":5737,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n扑斷隻腳再撐返高<br />\n諗起都腳到仆街<br />\n你有一百萬 亂Fing <br />\n得唔信溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8968116f22b95765ffa79ff9d3a0d06ae9